{"tid":1518810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，捱過左好多劫，今次唔係捱唔到嘛？？","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:32:10.000Z","uid":199829,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"39c082e0ce5f4a2d9c7876e6b703ca175bf48013","tid":1518810,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"自69以黎，政府中共同埋黑警不斷轉玩法去搞散運動，每一次佢地出招我地都拆解到。<br />\n<br />\n未入9月，佢地又開始轉玩法：<br />\n大搜捕，議員、平民、前線，咩人都拉；白色恐怖，企業白色恐怖、公務員白色恐怖、學校白色恐怖將會陸續出現<br />\n<br />\n616後：政府用暫緩惡法意圖結束運動，但我們提出五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n71後：政府想用拖延計去拖散運動，但我地將運動帶入社區，成功喚起街坊加入抗爭團隊，其後出現各區連儂牆，成功增加運動保鮮度，達致遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n721：黑警與黑社會聯手恐怖襲擊，但沒有嚇退我地，反而拉壟到淺藍入伍及成功變成黑警其中一個大核彈之一<br />\n<br />\n726：首個遊行批出反對通知書，及後嘅遊行示威都用反對通知書意圖阻嚇和理非，但最後元朗嘅30萬人行街，818嘅170萬人流水式集會無阻集會意志<br />\n<br />\n824及825：狗鐵開始配合黑警停駛關站，意圖阻止民眾上街，但亦無阻民眾遊行意欲<br />\n<br />\n現在：各階層白色恐怖彌漫、全民大搜捕、放風出緊急法將會係呢個9月政府變陣嘅招數<br />\n<br />\n每次政府變招，我地都會有氣餒，有唔知點算好嘅情況出現，但睇返轉頭，我地捱過左好多次變招，今次我都相信大家可以捱過的！！"},{"pid":"6a764d1211fc0f4f9dd866529586cec8a1d5035f","tid":1518810,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=c291610c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=ab9134a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=5c91d965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUirPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=0d4a8ef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"081d235bc4484382c66604365409c6b8b6afc4b8","tid":1518810,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e8eb6696cbdb0a40146555963a12a5f20ef8e9","tid":1518810,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ca7c896dba20fc75a41304197ff014a35c40a1","tid":1518810,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f657aa328e32e28c1a43009e4c1ab1f56ac92720","tid":1518810,"uid":199829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9e69838bc27cbd8e5c276931a8beee0cd1d0f3